==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-good_morning.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Expression===
'''[[good]] [[morning]]'''

# A greeting said when meeting somebody for the first time in the morning.
# For a person who is too concerned about its usage, Good Morning can also be used to greet a  person when the meeting happens for the '''first''' time '''at any point''' of the day.The same is bolstered by British English

